    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.h7ktzr7anfh382xu]{brand}, except that it inflicts 1d6 points of damage when applied and cannot be removed, even temporarily. In addition, a greater <em>brand</em> blazes as bright as a torch when brought within 30 feet of a visible symbol of your faith. While the symbol is blazing, the recipient is sickened.</p>\n<p>Like the effects of @Compendium[pf1.spells.lsboosfk26m0ycqv]{bestow curse}, a greater <em>brand</em> cannot be dispelled, but it can be removed by any means that removes a @Compendium[pf1.spells.3jaumkutti1ytulq]{mark of justice}.</p>"
